Description: Ernie Ball Music Man BFR Luke III in the quilted top Hazel finish with birdseye maple neck and rosewood fingerboard. This guitar is virtually new. It's been set up with 9s and is a joy to play. It has the volume pot push/push pre-amp that gives a 12dB boost. It's a spectacular looking and playing guitar. Buyer pays shipping. I will only ship to the continental US.
